messages.message: Gotcha. I created a new sandbox from the ibdev-backend template, and it's missing the aihub_guest user and sample files.
@Xindi Xu Do you know how the aihub_guest user is created?

Based on this doc, you have to create this manually
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IndR3LfrkciQR-M_of76Rdxd9uAIMRSaXRirhTLyBcw/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.ivkgzs12jxth
Loginless mode is not needed in ST AIHub envs. Probably that's why we don't create this in the post-install-action
